extends layouts/main

block content
  h2 Password Successfully Recovered
  p Hello #{userName || 'User'},
  p Your password has been successfully recovered and updated.
  p You can now login with your new password and access your account normally.
  p For security reasons, we recommend that you:
  ul
    li Change your password after logging in
    li Use a strong, unique password
    li Enable two-factor authentication if available
  p If you didn't request this password recovery, please contact our support team immediately.
  p Best regards,
  p The Security Team
